{
  "stem": "2690.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, Sophie, the people were screaming for their life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they were-- after that, they took them to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's where my husband would have eventually ended up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But he came home, thank God.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was very careful always to wear the star.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in 1942, we were taken, at that time, in the-- on the 25th of September, they came at night with a paper for myself, my husband, and my child, to go to where the Germans were.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we would go to a camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I asked them very nicely, I just put my child to bed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I worked very hard today in the store.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It happened to be very busy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my husband and I are really very tired, and my child just went to sleep.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Will you come back tomorrow?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we-- that same day, my dad had given the Germans a lot of money to get what they call a [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was the name that meant a paper that you would not be picked up, and you would go to Portugal.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they said, who do you think you are, that you can order us around?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, no, I'm not ordering you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm asking you to come back tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because then I knew I would have the paper in my hand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said, no, you have to come with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So right away, we had to go in-- in a wagon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they took us to a pace in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And from there, they put you on the train to Westerbork, to the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not a word.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing is said.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because you're Jewish, of course.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I never thought of that, so I had nothing ready at that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
